/*
 * This codes reads all of the channels from out transmitter and packs them into our PPM signal
 * For testing purposes, we can add Serial prints for all of the values to check if everything is working correctly
 * The roll on my transmitter is broken (bad potentiometer), so I've programmed the receiever to ignore that channel
 * unless a specific AUX is activated
 */

/* 
